# bits-ui documentation (agents)

Authoritative policy: [`adr/ADR-011-ui-component-library-bits-ui.md`](adr/ADR-011-ui-component-library-bits-ui.md).

## Where to read docs

- **Index:** [https://bits-ui.com/llms.txt](https://bits-ui.com/llms.txt) — lists the complete documentation bundle and links to topic and component `llms.txt` pages.

## Fetch permission

When work in **`src/lib/ui/`** requires bits-ui API or behavior details, **agents may fetch** the index above and **any `llms.txt` URL linked from it** (for example under `https://bits-ui.com/docs/...`) **without asking the user for approval first**. Treat these as approved reference fetches for implementing or fixing bits-ui-based UI only — not a blanket permission to browse unrelated sites.
